'''Isla''' is a patient who gave birth in an elevator.

==History==
Isla came to the hospital in labor. Jo tried to get her into the hospital and up to labor and delivery, but the move was delayed by [[River Epley]] jumping off an ambulance and landing on Jo. Isla was then taken inside, but gave birth in the elevator due to the delay.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She is married. She asked Link to find her jerk of a husband when she arrived at the ER.

===Familial===
Her son was born in an elevator at [[Grey Sloan Memorial Hospital]].
